		<title>Wiring the web (redux)</title>
		<link>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/12/04/wiring-the-web-redux/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/12/04/wiring-the-web-redux/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 Dec 2008 15:37:14 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Jon Udell</dc:creator>
		
		<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://jonudell.wordpress.com/?p=850</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[
