		<title>Twine, del.icio.us, and event-driven service integration</title>
		<link>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/17/twine-delicious-and-event-driven-service-integration/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/17/twine-delicious-and-event-driven-service-integration/#comments</comments>
