		<title>Where the oil comes from: Not from where I thought</title>
		<link>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/09/where-the-oil-comes-from-not-from-where-i-thought/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/09/where-the-oil-comes-from-not-from-where-i-thought/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 09 Nov 2008 18:34:33 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Jon Udell</dc:creator>
		
