		<link>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/03/for-granicus-transparent-democracy-is-just-business-as-usual/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.jonudell.net/2008/11/03/for-granicus-transparent-democracy-is-just-business-as-usual/#comments</comments>
